snippet: Uncertainty about earnings and the negotiations on the debt ceiling have cooled investor enthusiasm, said Bucky Hellwig of BB&T Wealth Management.
abstract: Stocks fall, retreating further from previous week's rally after federal budget deal, as companies begin to report quarterly results.
lead_paragraph: Uncertainty about earnings and the negotiations on the debt ceiling have cooled investor enthusiasm, said Bucky Hellwig of BB&T Wealth Management.
